vernac_cmds: Inductive le_ni : nested_imps -> nested_imps -> Prop := | Le_NI_Nil : le_ni NNil NNil | Le_NI_Cons_NN : forall (x : nimp) (ni1 ni2 : nested_imps), le_ni ni1 ni2 -> le_ni (Undecorated x :: ni1) (Undecorated x :: ni2) | Le_NI_Cons_DN : forall (x : nimp) (k : kripke_tree) (ni1 ni2 : nested_imps), le_ni ni1 ni2 -> le_ni (Decorated x k :: ni1) (Undecorated x :: ni2) | Le_NI_Cons_DD : forall (x : nimp) (k : kripke_tree) (ni1 ni2 : nested_imps), le_ni ni1 ni2 -> le_ni (Decorated x k :: ni1) (Decorated x k :: ni2).
Lemma in_k_le : forall (ni1 ni2 : nested_imps) (x : nimp) (k : kripke_tree), le_ni ni1 ni2 -> In (Decorated x k) ni2 -> In (Decorated x k) ni1.
intros ni1 ni2 x k le12.
elim le12; clear le12 ni1 ni2.
intros x' ni1 ni2 le12 ih in_k.
intros x' k' ni1 ni2 le12 ih in_k.
intros x' k' ni1 ni2 le12 ih in_k.
Lemma le_ni_refl : forall ni : nested_imps, le_ni ni ni.
intros ni; elim ni; clear ni.
intros a; case a; clear a.
Lemma le_ni_trans : forall ni1 ni2 ni3 : nested_imps, le_ni ni1 ni2 -> le_ni ni2 ni3 -> le_ni ni1 ni3.
elim le12; clear le12 ni1 ni2.
intros x ni1 ni2 le12 ih ni3 le23.
intros x k ni1 ni2 le12 ih ni3 le23.
intros x k ni1 ni2 le12 ih ni3 le23.

Inductive filter_deco_spec (i : Int) (N : nested_imps) : Set := Filter_Deco_Spec_Intro : forall ni1 : nested_imps, le_ni N ni1 -> (forall (x : nimp) (k : kripke_tree), In (Decorated x k) ni1 -> forces_t k (Atom i)) -> filter_deco_spec i N.
Lemma filter_deco : forall (i : Int) (ni : nested_imps), filter_deco_spec i ni.
intros a; case a; clear a.
intros d; case d; clear d.
apply Filter_Deco_Spec_Intro with (Decorated x (node atoms (AVL_intro unit t avl_t) succs) :: ni1).
simpl in |- *; intros x' k' in_k0.

Inductive eqv_ni : nested_imps -> nested_imps -> Prop := | Eqv_NI_Nil : eqv_ni NNil NNil | Eqv_NI_Cons_NN : forall (x : nimp) (ni1 ni2 : nested_imps), eqv_ni ni1 ni2 -> eqv_ni (Undecorated x :: ni1) (Undecorated x :: ni2) | Eqv_NI_Cons_DN : forall (x : nimp) (k : kripke_tree) (ni1 ni2 : nested_imps), eqv_ni ni1 ni2 -> eqv_ni (Decorated x k :: ni1) (Undecorated x :: ni2) | Eqv_NI_Cons_DD : forall (x : nimp) (k k' : kripke_tree) (ni1 ni2 : nested_imps), eqv_ni ni1 ni2 -> eqv_ni (Decorated x k :: ni1) (Decorated x k' :: ni2) | Eqv_NI_Cons_ND : forall (x : nimp) (k : kripke_tree) (ni1 ni2 : nested_imps), eqv_ni ni1 ni2 -> eqv_ni (Undecorated x :: ni1) (Decorated x k :: ni2).
Lemma eqv_ni_trans : forall ni1 ni2 ni3 : nested_imps, eqv_ni ni1 ni2 -> eqv_ni ni2 ni3 -> eqv_ni ni1 ni3.
elim eqv12; clear eqv12 ni1 ni2.
intros x ni1 ni2 eqv12 ih ni3 eqv23.
intros x k ni1 ni2 eqv12 ih ni3 eqv23.
intros x k k' ni1 ni2 eqv12 ih ni3 eqv23.
intros x k ni1 ni2 eqv12 ih ni3 eqv23.
Lemma le_eqv : forall ni1 ni2 : nested_imps, le_ni ni1 ni2 -> eqv_ni ni1 ni2.
intros ni1 ni2 le12; elim le12; clear le12 ni1 ni2.
intros x ni1 ni2 le12 ih; apply Eqv_NI_Cons_NN; assumption.
intros x k ni1 ni2 le12 ih; apply Eqv_NI_Cons_DN; assumption.
intros x k ni1 ni2 le12 ih; apply Eqv_NI_Cons_DD; assumption.
Lemma eqv_sym : forall ni1 ni2 : nested_imps, eqv_ni ni1 ni2 -> eqv_ni ni2 ni1.
intros ni1 ni2 eqv12; elim eqv12; clear eqv12 ni1 ni2.
intros x ni1 ni2 eqv12 ih; apply Eqv_NI_Cons_NN; assumption.
intros x k ni1 ni2 eqv12 ih; apply Eqv_NI_Cons_ND; assumption.
intros x k k' ni1 ni2 eqv12 ih; apply Eqv_NI_Cons_DD; assumption.
intros x k ni1 ni2 eqv12 ih; apply Eqv_NI_Cons_DN; assumption.
Lemma ge_eqv : forall ni1 ni2 : nested_imps, le_ni ni2 ni1 -> eqv_ni ni1 ni2.

Lemma eqv_ni_rec : forall P : nested_imps -> nested_imps -> Set, P NNil NNil -> (forall (x : nimp) (ni1 ni2 : nested_imps), eqv_ni ni1 ni2 -> P ni1 ni2 -> P (Undecorated x :: ni1) (Undecorated x :: ni2)) -> (forall (x : nimp) (k : kripke_tree) (ni1 ni2 : nested_imps), eqv_ni ni1 ni2 -> P ni1 ni2 -> P (Decorated x k :: ni1) (Undecorated x :: ni2)) -> (forall (x : nimp) (k k' : kripke_tree) (ni1 ni2 : nested_imps), eqv_ni ni1 ni2 -> P ni1 ni2 -> P (Decorated x k :: ni1) (Decorated x k' :: ni2)) -> (forall (x : nimp) (k : kripke_tree) (ni1 ni2 : nested_imps), eqv_ni ni1 ni2 -> P ni1 ni2 -> P (Undecorated x :: ni1) (Decorated x k :: ni2)) -> forall ni1 ni2 : nested_imps, eqv_ni ni1 ni2 -> P ni1 ni2.
intros P base step_nn step_rn step_rr step_nr ni1.

Inductive inf_deco_spec (ni1 ni2 : nested_imps) : Set := Inf_Deco_Spec_Intro : forall ni : nested_imps, le_ni ni ni1 -> eqv_ni ni ni2 -> (forall (x : nimp) (k : kripke_tree), In (Decorated x k) ni -> In (Decorated x k) ni1 \/ In (Decorated x k) ni2) -> inf_deco_spec ni1 ni2.
Lemma inf_deco : forall ni1 ni2 : nested_imps, eqv_ni ni1 ni2 -> inf_deco_spec ni1 ni2.
elim eqv12; clear eqv12 ni1 ni2.
intros x ni1 ni2 eqv12 ih.
elim (inf x' k' H); clear inf H.
intros x k ni1 ni2 eqv12 ih.
apply Inf_Deco_Spec_Intro with (Decorated x k :: ni).
elim (inf x' k' H); clear inf H.
intros x k k' ni1 ni2 eqv12 ih.
apply Inf_Deco_Spec_Intro with (Decorated x k :: ni).
elim (inf x0 k0 H); clear inf H.
intros x k ni1 ni2 eqv12 ih.
apply Inf_Deco_Spec_Intro with (Decorated x k :: ni).
elim (inf x0 k0 H); clear inf H.
Remark eqv_nimps_eq : forall ni1 ni2 : nested_imps, eqv_ni ni1 ni2 -> nested_imps2nimps ni1 = nested_imps2nimps ni2.
elim eqv; clear eqv ni1 ni2; simpl in |- *.
intros x ni1 ni2 eqv ih; rewrite ih; trivial.
intros x k ni1 ni2 eqv ih; rewrite ih; trivial.
intros x k1 k2 ni1 ni2 eqv ih; rewrite ih; trivial.
intros x k ni1 ni2 eqv ih; rewrite ih; trivial.

Lemma in_ngamma_eqv : forall (work : nf_list) (ds : disjs) (ni1 ni2 : nested_imps) (ai : atomic_imps) (a : atoms) (c : normal_form), eqv_ni ni1 ni2 -> in_ngamma work ds ni1 ai a c -> in_ngamma work ds ni2 ai a c.
intros work ds ni1 ni2 ai a c eqv12 ini1.
apply in_ngamma_ni_eq with ni1; try assumption.

Lemma in_ngamma_le : forall (work : nf_list) (ds : disjs) (ni1 ni2 : nested_imps) (ai : atomic_imps) (a : atoms) (c : normal_form), le_ni ni1 ni2 -> in_ngamma work ds ni1 ai a c -> in_ngamma work ds ni2 ai a c.
intros work ds ni1 ni2 ai a c le12 in_ngamma.

Lemma in_ngamma_ge : forall (work : nf_list) (ds : disjs) (ni1 ni2 : nested_imps) (ai : atomic_imps) (a : atoms) (c : normal_form), le_ni ni2 ni1 -> in_ngamma work ds ni1 ai a c -> in_ngamma work ds ni2 ai a c.
intros work ds ni1 ni2 ai a c le21 in_ngamma.
Inductive le_app_spec (ni1 : nested_imps) (n : nat) : Set := Le_App_Spec_Intro : forall ni11 ni12 : nested_imps, ni1 = ni11 ++ ni12 -> length ni11 = n -> le_app_spec ni1 n.
Lemma le_app0 : forall ni1 ni21 ni22 : nested_imps, le_ni ni1 (ni21 ++ ni22) -> le_app_spec ni1 (length ni21).
intros le; elimtype False; inversion_clear le.
simpl in |- *; intros x' ni1 le1.

Lemma le_ni_app_nn : forall (ni1 ni2 ni3 ni4 : nested_imps) (x : nimp), length ni1 = length ni3 -> le_ni (ni1 ++ ni2) (ni3 ++ ni4) -> le_ni (ni1 ++ Undecorated x :: ni2) (ni3 ++ Undecorated x :: ni4).
intros ni1 ni2 ni3 ni4 x.
intros ni3; case ni3; clear ni3.
intros ni3; case ni3; clear ni3.
simpl in |- *; intros len le; inversion_clear len.
simpl in |- *; intros y' ni3 len le.

Lemma le_ni_app_dn : forall (ni1 ni2 ni3 ni4 : nested_imps) (x : nimp) (k : kripke_tree), length ni1 = length ni3 -> le_ni (ni1 ++ ni2) (ni3 ++ ni4) -> le_ni (ni1 ++ Decorated x k :: ni2) (ni3 ++ Undecorated x :: ni4).
intros ni1 ni2 ni3 ni4 x k.
intros ni3; case ni3; clear ni3.
intros ni3; case ni3; clear ni3.
simpl in |- *; intros len le; inversion_clear len.
simpl in |- *; intros y' ni3 len le.

Lemma le_ni_app_dd : forall (ni1 ni2 ni3 ni4 : nested_imps) (x : nimp) (k : kripke_tree), length ni1 = length ni3 -> le_ni (ni1 ++ ni2) (ni3 ++ ni4) -> le_ni (ni1 ++ Decorated x k :: ni2) (ni3 ++ Decorated x k :: ni4).
intros ni1 ni2 ni3 ni4 x k.
intros ni3; case ni3; clear ni3.
intros ni3; case ni3; clear ni3.
simpl in |- *; intros len le; inversion_clear len.
simpl in |- *; intros y' ni3 len le.
